---
// SVG icons inline
const ArrowRightIcon = `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>`;

const CheckIcon = `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>`;
---

<section class="py-24 bg-[#0f0f0f] border-t border-b border-gray-800">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-industrial text-center text-white mb-16 uppercase">
      Como funciona a parceria
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-0 border border-gray-700 bg-[#0a0a0a]">
      
      <!-- Client Column -->
      <div class="p-10 border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-gray-700 relative group overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gray-600 group-hover:bg-gray-400 transition-colors"></div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-industrial text-gray-400 mb-8 uppercase tracking-wide">
          Para o Seu Cliente
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gray-800 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 text-white" set:html={CheckIcon} />
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Aumento imediato de conversão (Lead -&gt; Agendamento).</p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gray-800 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 text-white" set:html={CheckIcon} />
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Fim da briga Marketing vs. Vendas.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gray-800 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 text-white" set:html={CheckIcon} />
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Sensação de que a <strong class="text-white">Sua Agência</strong> resolveu o problema de faturamento dele.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Agency Column -->
      <div class="p-10 relative bg-yellow-900/5 group overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-yellow-600 group-hover:bg-yellow-400 transition-colors"></div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-industrial text-yellow-500 mb-8 uppercase tracking-wide flex items-center gap-2">
          Para a Sua Agência <div class="w-5 h-5" set:html={ArrowRightIcon} />
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 text-yellow-500" set:html={CheckIcon} />
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-white block mb-1 font-industrial">Setup Fee & Markup</strong>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Você pode cobrar um markup sobre o meu serviço ou repassar direto como custo operacional.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 text-yellow-500" set:html={CheckIcon} />
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-white block mb-1 font-industrial">Retenção Brutal</strong>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Cliente que vende não cancela. O churn despenca.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 text-yellow-500" set:html={CheckIcon} />
            </div>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-white block mb-1 font-industrial">Diferencial Competitivo</strong>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">"Nós somos a única agência que entrega Leads + Máquina de Vendas".</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

